## Spec Files

All phase specs live in `docs/archive/phases/phase-N-spec.md`.
Phase ZIPs live in `releases/phase-zips/iHouse-Core-Docs-Phase-N.zip`.
Handoffs live in `releases/handoffs/handoff_to_new_chat Phase-N.md`.
